channel.title: Moparscape Running Error
channel.description:
Yesterday I was on Moparscape, playing on my server. Today, when I went to go open Moparscape, I got an error in a batch file window stating "Error:could not open 'C:/Program files/Java/jdk1.5(2)/lib/i386/jvm.cfg' Press any key to continue"
Any solutions to this?
